   "body" : "The current code fails to set the x_only flag on the public key inside `pk()` inside `tr()` descriptors. This leads to the wrong scriptPubKeys being generated from such an inferred descriptor (converting said descriptor to string and parsing it back however fixes it, so this is probably not actually observable anywhere).\r\n\r\nThis was discovered while adding unit tests to descriptor_tests that cover various aspects of `tr()` descriptors, which are now also added here.",
